title: Ryno, Sarge and Doctor K: A look back at Mets-Cubs in '84
text: > Sports Ryno, Sarge and Doctor K: A look back at Mets-Cubs in '84 FILE - In this Sept. 16, 1984 file photo, New York Mets' outfielder Darryl Strawberry is safe at third as Chicago Cubs' third baseman Ron Cey misses a wild throw from outfielder Thad Bosley during fifth inning of a baseball game in Chicago. The Mets and Cubs, who are playing each other in Game 3 of the NL Championship Series on Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015, had a memorable race for the NL East title in 1984. (AP Photo/Chuck Bennett, File)
